# 02 - Research Pipeline
# Multi-step research with sequential goals

NAME research-pipeline
INPUT topic
INPUT depth DEFAULT "comprehensive"

GOAL research "Research $topic at a $depth level. Focus on: key facts (3-5), brief history, current state. Spawn as many subagents as you need. Write all your raw research content to research-raw.md."
GOAL analyze "Analyze the research output. Identify key patterns or insights. Keep analysis concise. Note that analysis must pull interesting information from the raw research; a kind of 'read between the lines' approach. Spawn subagents as needed. Write all your research analysis to research-analysis.md"
GOAL synthesize "Write a structured report (500-800 words) using output of online research and analysis steps. Have clear sections. Save to research-output.md."

RUN pipeline USING research, analyze, synthesize
